attributes.review: This is by far the worst app ever🤬🤬!! The app took 45 days to download🙄. Many strange things starting occurring shortly after downloading this app. My pet fish died out of nowhere... rest easy Esteban Julio Ricardo Montoya de la Rosa Ramírez Jr. 😔💔 yuh🤞. Then all of my food starting turning a bright orange😳! And It would stain my fingers and mouth! I constantly hear these soft chants of someone saying “𝓜𝓪𝓴𝓮🇺🇸 𝓐𝓶𝓮𝓻𝓲𝓬𝓪🇺🇸 𝓰𝓻𝓮𝓪𝓽🇺🇸𝓪𝓰𝓪𝓲𝓷🇺🇸”. Things just kept getting worse and worse😢. Some nights I would wake up feeling like someone was Staring at me but I would go right back to sleep because I figured it was just my imagination. But that feeling continued. I always felt like someone was watching me. One night I decided to investigate. I set up a hidden camera and watched it the next day. There was an old man covered head to toe in Cheetos dust. I thought to myself  “no way! It couldn’t be Donald Trump!😳🤭” And then out of nowhere someone comes up behind me, puts a bag over my head, ties me up, and throws me in a van😩. Anyway, now I’m locked up somewhere😗. I think Bunker Boi kidnapped me and threw me in here. There’s a couple other kids there, they’re pretty cool tbh😎.  Tryna see if maybe my family is down here too😒. But anyway yuh... don’t download.
